## 🚀 Deployment Commands Cheat Sheet

### Build & Deploy (Quick Reference)

```bash
# Frontend build
cd frontend && npm run build

# Upload to server (via rsync)
rsync -avz dist/ user@server:/var/www/ldm-erp/frontend/

# Backend deployment
rsync -avz api/ user@server:/var/www/ldm-erp/api/

# Restart services
sudo systemctl reload nginx
sudo systemctl restart php8.2-fpm

# Clear cache
php api/cache-clear.php
```

---

## 🐛 Troubleshooting

### Frontend Issues

**404 on page refresh:**
- Check .htaccess rewrite rules
- Verify NGINX try_files configuration

**Assets not loading:**
- Check base path in [vite.config.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/vite.config.ts)
- Verify file permissions (755/644)

**API calls failing:**
- Check CORS configuration
- Verify API_URL environment variable

### Backend Issues

**500 Internal Server Error:**
- Check PHP error logs
- Verify .htaccess syntax
- Check file permissions

**Database connection failed:**
- Verify .env credentials
- Check MySQL service status
- Confirm database exists

**JWT authentication failing:**
- Verify JWT_SECRET is set
- Check token expiration time
- Review CORS headers

